of%20us%20will%20agree%20that%20we%20will%20not%20bring%20soldiers%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20the%20boundary.%20And%20we%20will%20never%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20there'll%20be%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20understanding%20which%20started%20in%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20actually%20was%20reflected%20in%20several%20agreements.%20And%20those%20agreements%20gave%20the%20relationship%20stability%20based%20on%20which%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20the%20relationship%20went%20forward%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20for%20reasons%20still%20not%20clear%20to%20us%2C%20these%20agreements%20were%20broken%20in%202020.%20And%20we%20had%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20China%20nose-dived%20significantly%20following%20the%20deadly%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711555920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fpbi2ebo8_s-jaishankar_625x300_24_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnormalcy-in-ties-with-china-will-only-be-achieved-based-on-based-on-the-traditional-troop-deployment-s-jaishankar-5322177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20ties%20with%20China%20will%20only%20be%20achieved%20based%20on%20the%20traditional%20deployment%20of%20troops%20and%20will%20be%20the%20prerequisite%20for%20the%20relationship%20with%20Beijing%20in%20the%20future%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%22%2C%22auth