3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20one%20of%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20kind%20of%20email%20from%20your%20boss%20is%20absolutely%20spine-tingling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20thing%20that%20all%20employees%20can%20agree%20on%2C%20one%20solidarity%20among%20the%20working%20man%20and%20woman%3A%20There%20are%20some%20messages%20from%20your%20boss%20that%20are%20absolutely%20terrifying%20%E2%80%94%20chief%20among%20those%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20have%20a%20minute%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEOs%20(and%20bosses)%20have%20a%20unique%20way%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fkatienotopoulos%2Fi-tried-emailing-like-your-boss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemailing%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20It%20tends%20to%20be%20short%20and%20immediate.%20A%20response%20within%20minutes%2C%20short%20and%20to%20the%20point%2C%20none%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhope%20this%20email%20finds%20you%20well%26quot%3B%20filler.%20It's%20efficient%20but%20can%20be%20harrowing%20for%20employees%20who%20try%20to%20read%20sentiment%20between%20the%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20apparently%2C%20has%20his%20own%20specific%20way%20of%20being%20terrifying%20as%20a%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewly%20unsealed%20documents%20from%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20against%20Meta%20reveal%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-facebook-execs-decrypt-rival-apps-usage-snap-youtube-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZuckerberg%20directed%20his%20underlings%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20track%20user%20analytics%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20competitors%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20Snapchat%20back%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20basic%20gist%20from%20a%20story%20reported%20by%20my%20colleagues%20Kali%20Hays%20and%20Jack%20Newsham%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20acquired%20a%20company%20called%20Onavo%2C%20which%20had%20a%20user%20privacy%20app%20that%20tracked%20user%20data%20about%20other%20apps%20(ironic%2C%20eh%3F).%20This%20data%20had%20valuable%20information%20about%20which%20new%20apps%20were%20blowing%20up%2C%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20which%20Meta%20then%20went%20out%20and%20bought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20competitor%20Snapchat's%20user%20data%20was%20encrypted%2C%20which%20meant%20through%20Onavo%2C%20Facebook%20couldn't%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20Snapchat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20sent%20an%20email%20(which%20has%20now%20been%20revealed%20in%20the%20lawsuit)%20to%20a%20few%20Facebook%20employees%2C%20including%20Javier%20Olivan%20(now%20Meta's%20COO)%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20he%20wanted%20them%20to%20essentially%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20around%20that%20encryption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20emails%20in%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Zuckerberg%20wrote%20to%20three%20employees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWhenever%20someone%20asks%20a%20question%20about%20Snapchat%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20usually%20that%20because%20their%20traffic%20is%20encrypted%2C%20we%20have%20no%20analytics%20on%20them.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EGiven%20how%20quickly%20they're%20growing%2C%20it%20seems%20important%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20new%20way%20to%20get%20reliable%20analytics%20about%20them.%20Perhaps%20we%20need%20to%20do%20panels%20or%20write%20custom%20software.%20You%20should%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20put%20aside%20the%20alarming%20fact%20that%20Facebook's%20CEO%20appears%20to%20be%20directing%20his%20head%20of%20growth%20to%20do%20something%20to%20break%20or%20get%20around%20Snapchat's%20encryption%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esomething%20that%20even%20other%20Meta%20executives%20questioned%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.369872%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.369872.743.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocuments%3C%2Fa%3E%20unsealed%20in%20the%20suit.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20think%20of%20a%20good%20argument%20for%20why%20this%20is%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20then-head%20of%20security%20and%20privacy%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(And%20this%20was%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-divided-by-mark-zuckerberg-new-wartime-leadership-style-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZuckerberg%20considered%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeacetime%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20find%20absolutely%20bone-chilling%20is%20the%20last%20line%20in%20Zuck's%20email%3A%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20%3Cem%3Enothing%3C%2Fem%3E%20more%20terrifying%20to%20me%20than%20getting%20a%20message%20from%20your%20boss%20suggesting%20you%20should%20simply%20%3Cem%3Efigure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20something%3C%2Fem%3E.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20some%20people%20might%20find%20this%20kind%20of%20vague%20missive%20thrilling%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20empowering%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%20implies%20trust%20that%20you'll%20figure%20it%20out.%20To%20the%20credit%20of%20Meta%20employees%2C%20they%20did%20apparently%20figure%20it%20out.%20Whether%20that's%20a%20badge%20of%20project-management%20honor%20or%20a%20hugely%20problematic%20and%20scandalous%20action%2C%20well%2C%20I'm%20not%20judging.%20I%20just%20know%20I%20would%20absolutely%20crap%20my%20pants%20if%20I%20got%20that%20email%20from%20my%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-boss-email-terrifying-snap-lawsuit-facebook-meta-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711