e%20well%20received%20there%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-11568937%2FAlan-Titchmarsh-surprise-hit-NORTH-KOREA-Garden-Secrets-aired-state-TV.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20he%20said%20in%202022.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nknews.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fnorth-korean-tv-censors-blue-jeans-while-airing-british-gardening-show%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20specialist%20site%20NK%20News%20reported%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20when%20%26quot%3BGarden%20Secrets%26quot%3B%20is%20broadcast%20in%20North%20Korea%20it%20is%20dubbed%20and%20Korean%20music%20is%20played%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korea-tv-censors-benign-english-gardener-for-wearing-jeans-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711549419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660417801caec1275a69cf23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korea-tv-censors-benign-english-gardener-for-wearing-jeans-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22English%20TV%20presenter%20Alan%20Titchmarsh%20found%20himself%20the%20unlikely%20target%20of%20North%20Korean%20censorship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korea-tv-censors-benign-english-gardener-for-wearing-jeans-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20stock%20will%20fall%20another%2033%25%20because%20it's%20still%20expensive%20and%20lacks%20upside%20catalysts%2C%20Bernstein%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20speaking%20at%20a%20Tesla%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c