%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20its%20underperformance%2C%20Tesla%20still%20holds%20a%20massive%20premium%20against%20other%20auto%20firms%2C%20with%20a%20valuation%20that%20is%20six-fold%20higher%20than%20other%20manufacturers.%20That's%20because%20Tesla%20historically%20held%20a%20much%20higher%20growth%20rate%2C%20but%20that's%20less%20the%20case%20today%2C%20Bernstein%20said%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20said%2C%20today%20Tesla's%20margins%20are%20in%20line%20with%20or%20U.S.%20in%20some%20cases%20lower%20than%20US%2C%20Japanese%20and%20US%20OEMs%2C%20and%20its%20forward%20growth%20rate%20is%20more%20comparable%20to%20Toyota%20and%20Honda%2C%20and%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20BYD%2C%26quot%3B%20Sacconaghi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Tesla%20commands%20premium%20multiples%20above%20large-cap%20tech%20firms%2C%20it's%20margins%20are%20significantly%20lower%20among%20this%20cohort%20as%20well%2C%20Bernstein%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20note%2C%20softer%20demand%20is%20chipping%20away%20at%20Tesla's%20production%20volumes%2C%20as%20EV%20adoption%20decelerates%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%2C%20while%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Highland%20model%20in%20China%20failed%20to%20showcase%20a%20%26quot%3Bstep-change%26quot%3B%20in%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20lowered%20its%20production%20forecast%20to%201.98%20million%20for%20the%20year%2C%20against%20consensus%20of%202.06%20million.%20Tepid%20growth%20will%20continue%20into%202025.%20However%2C%20Tesla%20is%20still%20forecast%20to%20become%20the%20highest%20world's%20volume%20auto%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBullish%20investors%20may%20point%20to%20Tesla's%20full%20self-driving%20technology%20as%20a%20transformative%20venture%20that%20should%20justify%20its%20stock%20price%20overtime%2C%20but%20Bernstein%20notes%20that%20other%20manufacturers%20are%20also%20competing%20in%20this%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20unlikely%20that%20Tesla%20makes%20ground%20as%20a%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20as%20Waymo%20already%20dominates%20the%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20also%20pointed%20out%20Tesla's%20venture%20into%20robotics%20and%20AI%2C%20including%20the%20Optimus%20and%20Dojo%20announcements.%20But%20as%20with%20self-driving%2C%20the%20firm%20is%20already%20behind%2C%20with%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20downplaying%20Dojo%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%20cited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-price-crash-target-forecast-outlook-expensive-growth-bernstein-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711549389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66040c271caec1275a69cd90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftesla-stock-price-crash-target-forecast-outlook-expensive-growth-bernstein-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bernstein%20cut%20Tesla's%20target%20price%20to%20%24120%20from%20%24150%2C%20citing%20how%20expensive%20the%20stock%20is%20compared%20to%20other%20automakers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A190%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftesla-stock-price-crash-target-forecast-outlook-expensive-growth-bernstein-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Much%20of%20Putin's%20inner%20circle%20thinks%20Ukraine%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Moscow%20terror%20attack%2C%20badly%20undermining%20him%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putin%20russia%20economy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e72f556080194819fc7df6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMIKHAIL%20METZEL%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ff