'%20time%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20said%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20served%20late%2C%20and%20that%20he%20needed%20time%20to%20study%20the%20document.%20Senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20said%20the%20petition%20had%20been%20filed%20on%20March%2023.%20%26quot%3BDefects%20were%20cured%20later.%20I%20am%20sure%20Mr%20Raju%20does%20not%20want%20us%20to%20serve%20a%20defective%20copy%20to%20him...%20we%20shared%20petition%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%20his%20arrest%20had%20violated%20his%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20alleged%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArrest%20without%20interrogation%20shows%20the%20current%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20argued%2C%20underlining%20the%20AAP's%20claim%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20was%20timed%20to%20disrupt%20the%20party's%20campaign%20for%20next%20month's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Mr%20Raju%20said%20the%20ED%20sought%20to%20file%20replies%20on%20the%20main%20matter%20and%20on%20the%20petition%20for%20interim%20relief.%20When%20the%20court%20pointed%20out%20it%20had%20already%20said%20it%20will%20issue%20a%20notice%20in%20the%20former%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20interim%20relief%20also%2C%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%20If%20I%20am%20not%20entitled%20to%20file%20a%20reply%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20hear%20me.%20I%20can't%20be%20deprived%20of%20my%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20last%20week%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20has%20roiled%20his%20AAP%20and%20provoke