ries-shares-jump-4-mcap-again-reaches-rs-20-trn-mark-124032700705_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-industries-shares-jump-4-mcap-again-reaches-rs-20-trn-mark-124032700705_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHad%20Sensed...%26quot%3B%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Party%20Leader%20On%20Why%20He%20Dumped%20Lalu%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20pre-empted%20attempts%20of%20RJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20to%20%26quot%3Bhumiliate%26quot%3B%20allies%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20by%20calling%20off%20the%20alliance%2C%20a%20senior%20JD(U)%20leader%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%2C%20MLC%20and%20chief%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20made%20the%20claim%20referring%20to%20the%20RJD%20riding%20roughshod%20over%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20a%20dependable%20ally%20of%20the%20RJD%2C%20though%20the%20alliance%20has%20caused%20it%20to%20lose%20its%20own%20vote%20share%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20only%20time%20the%20Congress%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20its%20vote%20share%20in%20recent%20times%20was%20in%20the%202015%20Bihar%20Assembly%20polls%20when%20we%20too%20were%20part%20of%20that%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20headed%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20has%20unilaterally%20given%20party%20tickets%20to%20candidates%20for%20about%20a%20dozen%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20virtually%20blindsided%20and%20hoping%20against%20hope%20that%20the%20domineering%20ally%20will%20address%20its%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20type%20of%20alliance%20do%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20that%20the%20former%20is%20giving%20away%20party%20tickets%20to%20people%20at%20will%2C%20paying%20scant%20regard%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20latter%3F%26quot%3B%20Among%20the%20seats%20for%20which%20Mr%20Prasad%20has%20given%20tickets%20is%20Aurangabad%2C%20where%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20field%20former%20MP%20Nikhil%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20RJD%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20promised%20party%20ticket%20to%20JD(U)%20turncoat%20Bima%20Bharti%20from%20Purnea%2C%20a%20seat%20from%20which%20former%20MP%20Rajesh%20Ranjan%20alias%20Pappu%20Yadav%20is%20said%20to%20have%20got%20assurance%20of%20Congress%20ticket%20when%20he%20merged%20his%20Jan%20Adhikar%20Party%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20for%20nothing%20that%20our%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20been%20seeking%20early%20seat-sharing%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20He%20had%20sensed%20the%20RJD's%20plans%20to%20humiliate%20allies.%20So%20he%20taught%20them%20a%20lesson%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allusion%20was%20to%20Mr%20Kumar's%20exit%20from%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20that%20robbed%20RJD%20of%20power%20and%20stripped%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20son%20and%20heir%20apparent%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20of%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFishing%20in%20troubled%20waters%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20leader%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20show%20that%20it%20has%20spine.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20undertaken%20a%20country-wide%20padayatra%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20leader%20to%20have%20done%20so%20since%20the%201990s%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20managed%20to%20win%20a%20seat%20in%20Bihar%20while%20the%20RJD%2C%20despite%20seeming%20formidable%2C%20drew%20a%20blank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20the%20RJD%20will%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20by%20its%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Even%20if%20that%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20maintained%20that%20seat-sharing%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bannounced%20in%20an%20amicable%20fashion%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20joint%20statement%20by%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20BPCC%20president%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20they%20had%20said%20the%20candidates%20will%20be%20formally%20declared%20upon%20their%20return%20to%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711541880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fsd4pnr34_nitish-kumar-1200_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhad-sensed-nitish-kumar-party-leader-on-why-he-dumped-lalu-yadav-5320735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20pre-empted%20attempts%20of%20RJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20to%20%26quot%3Bhumiliate%26quot%3B%20allies%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20by%20calling%20off%20the%20alliance%2C%20a%20senior%20JD(U)%20leader%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhad-sensed-nitish-kumar-party-leader-on-why-he-dumped-lalu-yadav-5320735%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Baba%20Kalyani's%20nephew%2C%20niece%20move%20Pune%20court%20claiming%20share%20in%20group%20assets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711541760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F11%2Ffull%2F1660215179-1123.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbaba-kalyani-s-nephew-niece-move