india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20have%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20the%20women%20assessment%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F51427%2F11-social-incubators-helping-indian-social-entrepreneurs-transform-lives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego-to-market%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20opportunities%20for%20impact%20will%20put%20them%20on%20the%20right%20path%20to%20getting%20visibility%20for%20their%20startups%2C%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Kalyani%20breaks%20down%20the%20step-wise%20approach%20they%20followed%20in%20the%20first%20cohort.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20step%20was%20to%20identify%20startups%20offering%20innovative%20solutions%20across%20sectors%2C%20such%20as%20renewable%20energy%2C%20water%20and%20waste%20management%2C%20and%20climate-smart%20agriculture.%20We%20received%20140%20applications%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalyani%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20140%20applications%2C%2011%20startups%20that%20had%20%E2%80%9Csolutions%20ready%20to%20commercialise%E2%80%9D%20were%20selected%20and%20provided%20with%20four-week%20support%20filled%20with%20expert%20masterclasses%20and%20mentoring%20sessions%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20go-to-market%20plan%20(GTM).%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20term%2C%20they%20were%20evaluated%20by%20an%20expert%20jury%20that%20assessed%20their%20innovation%2C%20plans%20to%20scale%2C%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20proved%20their%20mettle%20made%20it%20to