5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20love%20snacking%20on%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20sold%20by%20your%20local%20vendor%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20then%20the%20next%20time%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20check%20on%20the%20oil%20he%20is%20using.%20According%20to%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%2C%20food%20business%20operators%20are%20supposed%20to%20discard%20vegetable%20oils%20after%20three%20times%20of%20frying%20or%20when%20their%20total%20polar%20compound%20(TPC)%20levels%20reach%2025%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20shocking%20is%20that%20though%20India%20generates%20three%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20%E2%80%98used%20cooking%20oil%E2%80%99%2C%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20it%20goes%20toward%20biodiesel%20production.%20What%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20rest%3F%20This%20startup%20is%20encouraging%20food%20outlets%20to%20channel%20the%20%E2%80%9Cused%E2%80%9D%20oil%20to%20them%20to%20convert%20into%20biodiesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Tvaran%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%2030%20tonnes%20of%20used%20cooking%20oil%20per%20month%20have%20been%20collected%20from%20over%20250%20vendors%20in%20South%20India%20and%20recycled%20into%20biofuel.%20Kalyani%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Tvaran%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20introduced%20to%20The%20Chennai%20Angels%20(TCA)%2C%20from%20whom%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20equity%20funding%20of%20Rs%203%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuccess%20stories%20like%20these%20fulfil%20the%20intention%20with%20which%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20conceptualised%20Tvaran.%20Kalyani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20simply%20zoomed%20in%20on%20this%20particular%20strategy.%20The%20shared%20interest%20when%20it%20came%20to%20supporting%20women%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20space%20helped%20us%20scale%20this%20idea%20into%20one%20that%20has%20impacted%20so%20many%20startups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20cohort%20enabled%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20to%20witness%20how%20market%20partnerships%20and%20support%20in%20implementing%20GTM%20strategies%20helped%20women-led%20businesses%2C%20as%20we%20advance%2C%20they%20say%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20fortify%20this%20cause.%20With%20the%20guiding%20belief%20that%20inventions%20are%20critical%20to%20driving%20change%2C%20the%20broader%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20these%20inventions%20get%20adopted%20while%20making%20communities%20resilient%20and%20improving%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202001%2C%20Villgro%20has%20backed%20387%20social%20enterprises%2C%20raising%20over%20Rs%204.7%20billion%20in%20investments.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20generated%208%2C175%20jobs%20and%20impacted%20over%2020.8%20million%20lives.%20Recognised%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20incubator%20in%202020%20by%20Invest%20India%20(DPIIT%2C%20GoI)%2C%20Villgro%20also%20won%20the%20DivHERsity%20awards%20in%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20picture%20credits%3A%20Villgro)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711022737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345161%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tvaran%20%E2%80%94%20a%20joint%20initiative%20by%20Cisco%20(India%20Cash%20Grant%20Program)%20and%20Villgro%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20unique%20programme%20empowering%20women%20entrepreneurs%20who%20are%20driving%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20sector%20by%20providing%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance.%20Here%20are%20seven%20such%20startups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20U.S.%20May%20Have%20Just%20Scored%20A%20Win%20Against%20China%20In%20The%20Battle%20Over%20A%20Key%20Mineral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Seven%20months%20after%20Beijing%20put%20trade%20restrictions%20on%20gallium%2C%20a%20Utah%20company%20found%20a%20major%20deposit%20of%20the%20metal.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711014316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65fb64a122000034004b842b.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fgallium-critical-minerals-us_n_65fb62fde4b07c954d54942c%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20months%20after%20Beijing%20put%20trade%20restrictions%20on%20gallium%2C%20a%20Utah%20company%20found%20a%20major%20deposit%20of%20the%20metal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fgallium-critical-minerals-us_n_65fb62fde4b07c954d54942c%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fgallium-critical-minerals-us_n_65fb62fde4b07c954d54942c%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fgallium-critical-minerals-us_n_65fb62fde4b07c954d54942c%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Green%20Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20IOT%20Biogas%20Plants%26nbsp%3BFuel%20Kitchens%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20Hewlett%20Packard%2C%20NTPC%20%26amp%3B%20more.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20in%20partnership%20with%20Greeneria%20Renewable%20Technologies%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bustling%20country%20of%20India%2C%20where%20rapid%20urbanisation%20meets%20the%20challenges%20of%20waste%20management%2C%20this%20visionary%20man%20from%20Bengaluru%20has%20been%20transforming%20the%20landscape%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeet%20M%20S%20R%20Kumar%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20with%20a%20global%20perspective%2C%20who%2C%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades%20abroad%2C%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20a%20mission%20%E2%80%94%20to%20introduce%20efficient%20waste%20management%20practices%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20urban%20areas%20using%20biogas%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20began%20with%20a%20realisation%20inspired%20by%20the%20success%20of%20biogas%20initiatives%20he%20witnessed%20in%20Canada%20and%20Germany.%20Despite%20facing%20initial%20scepticism%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F174765%2Fbihar-farmer-free-electricity-biogas-plant-woman-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeasibility%20of%20urban%20biogas%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20founded%20Greeneria%20in%202014%20to%20champion%20this%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Biogas%20Association%20(IBA)%2C%20which%20is%20instrumental%20in%20forming%20various%20policies%20along%20with%20ministries%20like%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%2C%20Petroleum%20Ministry%2C%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Water%20and%20Sanitation.%20The%20association%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20initiating%20the%20SATAT%20programme%20and%20the%20GOBARdhan%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%E2%80%99s%20projects%2C%20equipped%20with%20IoT%20technology%2C%20are%20spread%20across%20India%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20and%20major%20IT%20companies%20like%20Hewlett%20Packard%20and%20Capgemini%20to%20shopping%20malls%20like%20Forum%20and%20residential%20complexes.%20Greeneria%20proudly%20shares%20that%20they%20hold%20the%20record%20for%20the%20largest%20residential%20biogas%20system%20in%20India%2C%20providing%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20to%20Prestige%20Jindal%20City%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202262px)%20100vw%2C%202262px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222262%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%202262w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345429%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221697%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rise%20of%20biogas%20systems%20in%20urban%20waste%20management%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20time%20abroad%2C%20I%20observed%20efficient%20waste%20management%20practices%2C%20particularly%20biogas%20plants%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20inspired%20me%20to%20bring%20similar%20practices%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kumar%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202012%20with%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotivated%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247412%2Fbiogas-plant-cooking-gas-electricity-solid-waste-management-vegetable-fruit-wholesale-market-hyderabad-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20yield%20of%20biogas%20from%20urban%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20(4%25)%20compared%20to%20rural%20cow%20dung%20(2%25)%2C%20he%20advocated%20for%20its%20adoption%20in%20urban%20settings.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SATAT%20scheme%20promotes%20entrepreneurs%20to%20establish%20Compressed%20Bio%20Gas%20(CBG)%20plants.%20These%20plants%20produce%20and%20supply%20CBG%20to%20Oil%20Marketing%20Companies%20(OMCs)%20for%20use%20as%20automotive%20and%20industrial%20fuels.%20The%20GOBARdhan%20initiative%20involves%20various%20schemes%20and%20policies%2C%20focusing%20on%20converting%20organic%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20cattle%20dung%20and%20agricultural%20residue%20%E2%80%94%20into%20biogas%2C%20Compressed%20Biogas%20(CBG)%2C%20and%20Bio%20CNG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20shares%20that%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20is%20a%20landmark%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20waste%20management%20policies%2C%20and%20that%20one%20of%20their%20achievements%20coincided%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20mission%20%E2%80%94%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Rules%202016.%20Kumar%20explains%20that%20this%20regulation%2C%20particularly%20the%20Bulk%20Waste%20Generator%20Rule%2C%20became%20a%20game-changer%20for%20urban%20waste%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bulk%20Waste%20Generator%20Rule%20is%20crucial%20because%2C%20in%20any%20metropolitan%20area%2C%2060%25%20of%20waste%20comes%20from%20bulk%20generators%2C%20with%20only%2040%25%20originating%20from%20individual%20households%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20explaining%20that%20the%2060%25%20of%20bulk%20waste%20generators%20include%20places%20like%20fruit%20and%20vegetable%20markets%2C%20tech%20parks%2C%20wedding%20venues%2C%20shopping%20malls%2C%20apartments%2C%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201824px)%20100vw%2C%201824px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713.jpg%201824w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713-300x224.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713-500x373.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713-768x572.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713-1536x1144.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-014_11zon-1710998713-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345425%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221359%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20generators%20handle%20their%20waste%20on-site%20itself%2C%2060%25%20of%20waste%20can%20be%20stopped%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%20preventing%20environmental%20issues.%20Landfills%20are%20harmful%2C%20especially%20if%20organic%20waste%20ends%20up%20there%2C%20leading%20to%20pollution%2C%20groundwater%20contamination%2C%20and%20health%20problems%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20rule%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20consider%20each%20apartment%20producing%20one%20kg%20of%20waste.%20If%20there%20are%20100%20apartments%2C%20they%20collectively%20generate%20100%20kg%20of%20waste.%20According%20to%20the%20rule%2C%20any%20apartment%20complex%20with%20100%20or%20more%20units%20must%20implement%20a%20waste%20management%20system%3B%20otherwise%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20receive%20an%20occupational%20certificate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBulk%20Waste%20Generators%20(BWG)%2C%20who%20were%20initially%20indifferent%2C%20started%20showing%20interest%20because%20compliance%20with%20this%20rule%20became%20necessary%20for%20obtaining%20occupancy%20certificates%20and%20other%20licences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20this%20rule%20became%20a%20significant%20regulation%2C%20especially%20for%20managing%20organic%20waste%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20challenge.%20Unlike%20inorganic%20waste%20like%20plastic%20and%20paper%2C%20which%20can%20be%20easily%20recycled%20for%20profit%2C%20organic%20waste%20poses%20a%20more%20significant%20problem.%20However%2C%20if%20managed%20properly%2C%20organic%20waste%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20valuable%20gas%20and%20fertiliser%20through%20the%20process%20of%20biogas%20production.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249749%2Fpune-sustainable-home-biogas-plant-cooking-kitchen-waste-lpg-cylinder-price-save-money-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiogas%20serves%20as%20an%20equivalent%20to%20LPG%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20produces%20fertiliser%20as%20a%20byproduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20implementing%20this%20solution%20in%20apartments%2C%20hotels%2C%20tech%20parks%2C%20and%20for%20various%20bulk%20waste%20generators%2C%20even%20gaining%20interest%20from%20municipalities%20of%20cities%20like%20Prayagraj%2C%20Dharamshala%20and%20Belagavi.%20Our%20systems%20are%20equipped%20with%20IoT%20technology%2C%20allowing%20real-time%20monitoring%20of%20waste%20input%2C%20gas%20production%2C%20PH%20levels%2C%20electricity%20generation%2C%20and%20the%20health%20of%20the%20digester%2C%20providing%20valuable%20insights%20for%20efficient%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20environmental%20benefits%2C%20Greeneria%20emphasises%20the%20financial%20incentives%20of%20adopting%20biogas%20systems.%20Establishments%20with%20one-tonne-per-day%20biogas%20systems%20can%20earn%20around%20Rs%2075%2C000%20per%20year%20through%20carbon%20credits%2C%20adding%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20motivation%20for%20businesses%20to%20invest%20in%20sustainable%20waste%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-300x166.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-500x276.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-768x424.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-1536x848.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-2048x1131.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-032_11zon-1710998718-150x83.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345427%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20composting%20systems%2C%20which%20he%20says%20can%20be%20messy%2C%20emit%20strong%20odours%2C%20and%20attract%20pests%2C%20biogas%20systems%20offer%20a%20cleaner%20and%20more%20enclosed%20solution.%20In%20apartments%20or%20shopping%20malls%2C%20the%20unpleasant%20smell%20and%20associated%20issues%20like%20mosquito%20infestation%20are%20avoided%20with%20biogas%20systems.%20Despite%20the%20similar%20pricing%2C%20a%20life%20cycle%20analysis%20shows%20that%20biogas%20systems%20are%20more%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20decentralised%20waste%20management%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20centralised%20waste%20management%2C%20many%20governments%20invest%20in%20large%20compost%20plants%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20issues%20like%20methane%20emissions%2C%20if%20not%20properly%20managed.%20Methane%20is%20much%20more%20harmful%20than%20CO2%20when%20released%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%20So%20I%20advocated%20for%20a%20shift%20from%20large-scale%20composting%20to%20odour-free%20biogas%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20proposed%20the%20idea%20to%20various%20Government%20officials%2C%20emphasising%20the%20benefits%20of%20biogas%20systems.%20These%20systems%20not%20only%20produce%20gas%20but%20can%20also%20power%20community%20kitchens%20or%20gas%20power%20generators%20for%20streetlights%20and%20common%20area%20lighting.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20successfully%20implemented%20this%20concept%20in%20collaboration%20with%20more%20than%2030%20to%2040%20municipalities%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kumar%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20advocates%20decentralised%20waste%20management%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20much%20easier%20to%20segregate%20waste%20in%20smaller%20quantities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20informs%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20biogas%20systems%20becomes%20more%20economical%20as%20the%20number%20of%20apartments%20increases.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20a%201%2C000-apartment%20complex%2C%20the%20cost%20is%20approximately%20Rs%2035%20lakh.%20When%20divided%20among%20the%20apartments%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20one-time%20cost%20of%20Rs%203%2C500%20per%20apartment%2C%20serving%20them%20for%2035%20years%2C%20providing%20both%20electricity%20and%20fertiliser.%20Similarly%2C%20for%20a%20500-apartment%20complex%2C%20the%20cost%20per%20apartment%20is%20around%204%2C000%20rupees%2C%20making%20it%20an%20affordable%20investment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20this%20approach%20not%20only%20makes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179539%2Fbengaluru-biogas-from-kitchen-waste-bbmp-restaurant-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%20affordable%20for%20apartments%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20teaches%20children%20the%20importance%20of%20segregation%2C%20ensuring%20a%20cleaner%20environment%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20introduced%20a%20leasing%20model%2C%20making%20us%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20in%20India%20to%20offer%20leasing%20options%20for%20apartment%20associations%2C%20five-star%20hotels%2C%20tech%20parks%2C%20and%20other%20creditworthy%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20proudly%20hold%20the%20certification%20as%20the%20only%20IIT%20(Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology)%20certified%20biogas%20plant%20contractor%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20they%20are%20currently%20developing%20advanced%20segregation%20equipment.%20When%20municipal%20waste%20is%20input%20into%20the%20hopper%2C%20the%20output%20will%20be%2095%25%20segregated.%20The%20equipment%20will%20soon%20be%20available%20for%20market%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202420px)%20100vw%2C%202420px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222420%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715.jpg%202420w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-500x280.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-768x430.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-1536x859.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-2048x1146.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-001_11zon-1710998715-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345426%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221354%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFueling%20streets%2C%20corporations%2C%20and%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20stands%20out%20not%20only%20for%20its%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20but%20also%20for%20its%20technical%20expertise.%20The%20team%20has%20studied%20temperature-yield%20relationships%2C%20incorporating%20thermostat%20controls%2C%20and%20delved%20into%20the%20impact%20of%20agitation%20on%20yield.%20Their%20approach%20of%20incorporating%20both%20agitation%20and%20temperature%20controls%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20other%20biogas%20companies%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20says%20one%20of%20their%20significant%20projects%20is%20at%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20in%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20presidential%20acreages%2C%20surpassing%20the%20White%20House%20in%20size.%20%E2%80%9COur%20system%20efficiently%20manages%20its%20challenging%20waste%2C%20including%20horse%20dung!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Greeneria%20collaborated%20with%20Prayagraj%20Smart%20City%20to%20illuminate%20900%20streetlights%20using%2015%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste.%20In%20Dharamshala%20and%20Belagavi%2C%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste%20power%20450%20streetlights%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20corporations%20like%20Hewlett%20Packard%2C%20and%20Capgemini%20are%20making%20strides%20in%20waste%20management.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Hinjewadi%2C%20Pune%2C%206%2C000%20employees%20from%20Hewlett%20Packard%20generate%20one%20ton%20per%20day%20(TPD)%20of%20waste%2C%20producing%2035%20kg%20of%20gas%2C%20equivalent%20to%20expensive%20LPG.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181269%2Fifs-hero-biogas-sustainability-compost-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverting%20waste%20into%20biogas%20and%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20companies%20not%20only%20reduce%20LPG%20bills%20but%20also%20obtain%20organic%20fertiliser%20as%20an%20additional%20asset%20for%20their%20large%20campuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202081px)%20100vw%2C%202081px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222081%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F