nable%20India%20but%20also%20setting%20an%20example%20for%20businesses%20worldwide%20to%20embrace%20eco-friendly%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kumar%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20simplest%20ways%20to%20express%20patriotism%20towards%20India%20is%20by%20segregating%20our%20waste.%20Adopt%20a%20two%20or%20three-bin%20system.%20Use%20one%20bin%20for%20electronic%20waste%20and%20hazardous%20materials%2C%20another%20for%20organic%20waste%20(coloured%20green)%2C%20and%20a%20third%20for%20dry%20waste%20(coloured%20blue).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20make%20sustainability%20a%20part%20of%20our%20daily%20thought%20process%20and%20actions%20for%20a%20better%20environment%20for%20our%20children%20and%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Greeneria)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710999169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345419%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20of%20Greeneria%20Renwable%20Technology%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20Rajendra%20Kumar%20has%20transformed%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20waste%20management%20with%20IoT-equipped%20biogas%20projects%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345419%2Fbiogas-startup-greeneria-renewable-technology-turns-wet-waste-into-fuel-for-rashtrapati-bhavan-microsoft-hp%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Holi%2C%20Play%20With%20100%25%20Edible%20%26amp%3B%20Organic%20Colours%20Handcrafted%20By%20Bhil%20Tribals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHoli%20is%20almost%20here%2C%20ready%20to%20paint%20the%20country%20with%20its%20exquisite%20hues.%20The%20exuberant%20festival%20brings%20many%2