0we%20have%20such%20low%20numbers%20of%20tigers.%20Currently%2C%20we%20have%20just%20one%20tiger.%20This%20makes%20our%20tiger%20reserve%20different%20from%20the%20Kanha%2C%20Ranthambore%2C%20or%20Pilibhit%20tiger%20reserves.%20Because%20of%20the%20encroachment%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20progress%20eco-tourism%20in%20the%20region.%20Just%20a%20year%20back%2C%20we%20did%20not%20even%20have%20any%20gypsy%20safaris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20evicting%20encroachers%20to%20welcoming%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20field%20visits%20to%20the%20forest%2C%20Jain%20would%20often%20see%20large%20charred%20spots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20that%20giant%20100-year-old%20trees%20were%20burnt%20down%20to%20make%20huts%20and%20farmland.%20Immediately%2C%20I%20procured%20ISRO%20images%20from%202008%2C%202010%2C%20and%202012%2C%20and%20then%2C%20I%20conducted%20surveys%20using%20drones%20to%20assess%20the%20encroachment.%20After%20comparing%20both%20the%20images%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20the%20reserve%20was%20a%20dense%20forest%20until%202008.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20an%20open%20forest%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20was%20enacted%20and%20it%20stated%20that%20any%20member%20or%20community%20that%20primarily%20resided%20in%20forest%20land%20for%20bona%20fide%20livelihood%20needs%20before%2013%20December%2C%202005%2C%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20forest%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20the%20ISRO%20images%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20people%20settled%20here%20after%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20and%20at%20least%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20was%20recovered%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Jain%20informs%20that%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20necessary%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20encroachments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20dwellers%20seeking%20their%20documents%20in%20support%20of%20possessing%20the%20forest%20land.%20But%20when%20they%20did%20not%20cooperate%2C%20the%20officials%20asked%20them%20to%20vacate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20carrying%20eviction%20drives%20in%20this%20particular%20area%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20us.%20Our%20teams%20were%20attacked%20twice%20leading%20to%20injuries.%20My%20car%20was%20burnt%20down.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20me%20to%20see%20my%20own%20people%20being%20beaten%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20manage%20this%20situation%2C%20I%20announced%20on%20a%20loudspeaker%20that%20since